name: typescript
dbSeedCommand: psql "$BENCHMARK_DATABASE_URL" -v ON_ERROR_STOP=1 -c "TRUNCATE TABLE lamps RESTART IDENTITY CASCADE; INSERT INTO lamps (id, is_on, created_at, updated_at, deleted_at) SELECT uuid_generate_v5('6ba7b810-9dad-11d1-80b4-00c04fd430c8', 'lamp-' || g), (g % 2 = 0), NOW() - ((10001 - g) * INTERVAL '1 second'), NOW() - ((10001 - g) * INTERVAL '1 second'), NULL FROM generate_series(1, 10000) AS g;"
